data.title: C4V1
data.description:
An intro to the vehicles used by the Space Marines from the Land Speeder to the Land Raider.
Fun audio mishap in this weeks vid, my mic was having problems with my Pees, so if the first letter of a word cuts slightly then imagine a P is there. Doesn't happen all the time, but enough to be infuriating. Guess what I asked from the chaos gods for Christmas? 

Intro Music: 
Daniel Yount - Dark Times
